\par To become a god, a living creature must transcend the physical. The three steps of this transcendent path are known. First, he must come upon th
e awareness of secret aggression. Second, he must come upon the discernment of purpose within the animal shape. Third, he must experience death.
\par When this is done, the nascent god must find his own rebirth in a unique ordeal by which he discovers the one who summoned him.}{\fs20\cf1\insrsid15366585 
